      <title>DoValue 在 Elliott 交易中达成接近 4.5 亿欧元的融资协议</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-27/italian-debt-servicer-dovalue-nears-450-million-financing-for-elliott-deal</link>
      <description><![CDATA[意大利金融服务专业公司 DoValue SpA 即将与多家银行达成协议，提供约 4.5 亿欧元（合 4.89 亿美元）的信贷额度，这是完成与 Elliott Investment Management 旗下 Gardant SpA 服务部门合并的关键一步。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-27/italian-debt-servicer-dovalue-nears-450-million-financing-for-elliott-deal</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 27 May 2024 15:19:02 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>阿达尼明确 35 亿美元融资计划</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-27/adani-flagship-energy-unit-seek-board-nod-to-raise-2-billion</link>
      <description><![CDATA[亿万富翁高塔姆·阿达尼 (Gautam Adani) 帝国的旗舰企业阿达尼企业有限公司 (Adani Enterprises Ltd.) 已获得董事会批准，将筹集高达 1660 亿卢比（20 亿美元）的资金，而就在前一天，该集团的电力公用事业部门也获得了类似的 15 亿美元融资批准。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-27/adani-flagship-energy-unit-seek-board-nod-to-raise-2-billion</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 27 May 2024 10:31:39 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
